text: Gerard William "Gerry" Noonan (24 November 1951 – 26 June 2017) was an Australian rules footballer who played for the Fitzroy Football Club in the Victorian Football League (VFL). ==References== ==External links== * Category:1951 births Category:2017 deaths Category:Fitzroy Football Club players Category:Koroit Football Club players Category:Australian rules footballers from Victoria (Australia)
